DCB Holdings changes name to RHB Capital . The Kuala Lumpur Stock Exchange announced that financial services firm DCB Holdings Bhd has changed its name to RHB Capital Bhd . The shares of DCB will trade under the new name from Monday , the exchange said in a statement . " Share certificates bearing the name DCB Holdings Berhad will still be valid after the change of name , " it said . - - Kuala Lumpur newsroom ( 603 - 201 4813 ) 
